activity A
bind A: ax, ay
activity B
bind B: bs, bt
activity C
bind C: cfloat, enum
ax: integer between 0 and 100
ay: integer between 20 and 80
bs: integer between -100 and 100
bt: integer between 200 and 300
cfloat: float between 1.9 and 2.5
enum: true, false
Response[A, C] | |T.enum not in false, true |
Not Precedence[B, A] | | |
Init[C] |A.enum in true |
